@startuml
title UML state machine diagram

[*] --> ServiceCenterRegistration
ServiceCenterRegistration : exit / Account registered --> [*]

ServiceCenterRegistration --> ServiceCenterVerification
ServiceCenterVerification : exit / Login Service center --> [*]

ServiceCenterVerification --> ServiceCenterLogin
ServiceCenterLogin : exit / Logged In Successfully --> ServiceCenterHome

ServiceCenterHome : exit / Enter Damaged parts list --> Entering Damaged parts list
EnteringDamagedPartsList : exit / Return to service center home page --> ServiceCenterHome

ServiceCenterHome : exit / Expiry Notification page --> ExpiryNotification
ExpiryNotification : exit / Return to Service center home page --> ServiceCenterHome

ServiceCenterHome : exit / Updating Information list --> Updating parts Information
UpdatingPartsInformation : exit / Return to Service center home page --> ServiceCenterHome

ServiceCenterLogin : entry / Service Center not logged in --> ServiceCenterLogin
ServiceCenterLogin : do / Authenticate Service Center --> ServiceCenterLogin

ServiceCenterHome : exit / Logout --> Logout
Logout : exit / Logged out Successfully --> [*]

[*] --> CarOwnerRegistration
CarOwnerRegistration : exit / Account registered --> [*]

CarOwnerRegistration --> CarOwnerVerification
CarOwnerVerification : exit / Login Car Owner --> [*]

CarOwnerVerification --> CarOwnerLogin
CarOwnerLogin : exit / Logged In Successfully --> CarOwnerHome

CarOwnerHome : exit / View parts information --> ViewPartsInformation
ViewPartsInformation : exit / Return to Car owner home page --> CarOwnerHome

CarOwnerHome : exit / Service --> Service
Service : exit / Return to Car Owner home page --> CarOwnerHome

CarOwnerHome : exit / Report --> Report
Report : exit / Return to car owner home page --> CarOwnerHome

CarOwnerLogin : entry / Car owner not logged in --> CarOwnerLogin
CarOwnerLogin : do / Authenticate Car Owner --> CarOwnerLogin

Service : exit / Accept or deny request --> ChooseParts
ChooseParts : exit / Return to service page --> Service

Service : exit / Deny request --> [*]

MakePayment : entry / To make payments --> MakePayment
MakePayment : do / Make payments --> MakePayment
MakePayment : exit / Return to Service page --> Service
@enduml
